  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study designed to characterize the pharmacokinetics and comparative
      bioavailability of Roxane Laboratories' codeine sulfate tablets after oral administration of
      60 mg doses as 1 x 60 mg, 2 x 30 mg and 4 x 15 mg under fasted conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
